cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM

This paper presents a model for pose estimation and instance segmentation of people in images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The model uses a convolutional network for detection and prediction, which involves machine learning (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.LG) techniques. The model also allows for efficient inference, which involves robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
